{"tid":55190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★玩完了！支那人在該國的電工經驗，香港政府是承認的！","createTime":"2016-12-26T08:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-11T15:58:45.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cffdf9f7e0848c9f1acd3265a127db4341f1d46d","tid":55190,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:02:14.000Z","msg":"於中國內地取得的電力工作經驗，申請人除要遞交由有關僱主發出的工作經驗證明外，亦需同時提交中國內地公證處發出的機構資料核對證明，或內地的相關職業電工資格證明(如特種作業操作證或電工職業資格證書等)。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.emsd.gov.hk/tc/electricity_safety/how_to_apply/registering_as_an_electrical_worker_for_electrical/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.emsd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Felectricity_safety%2Fhow_to_apply%2Fregistering_as_an_electrical_worker_for_electrical%2Findex.html&d=hIPhOiaFzJJfBAMIi8cg%2BUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=c2aa020d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.emsd.gov.hk/tc/electricity_safety/how_to_apply/registering_as_an_electrical_worker_for_electrical/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"e10ee389ef6767326ad42edd4f7c7d4ad263edc4","tid":55190,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:03:41.000Z","msg":"香港人要5年才可以有A牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af09c8f0e8ffca4ac4007e29bf80260396186f8","tid":55190,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:08:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人要5年才可以有A牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家搞乜野專工專責咪一撚樣<br />\n明知香港大部份工人都係判上判咁做，唔會有好齊全工作證明，有d嫌煩既工人依家唔去申請，遲早無工做。無申請就代表佢唔係專業技工，就大條道理話缺乏專業技工去請外勞，實際上根本大把土炮工人<br />\n<br />\n個班中國黎既工人根本唔駛擔心申請唔到，佢話自己係中國做左10年野你根本吹佢唔脹，政府都唔會去查，但係你香港人有出入境紀錄，你想作都作唔到"},{"pid":"bce13f8ae8558f6cdf41ee204fada387c875e6cf","tid":55190,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:10:27